data.description: OUTDOOR OASIS and Meticulously maintained estate - Unbelievable opportunity to own your next home in the prestigious sought after Miramonte Ridge Subdivision. This breathtaking gem will not disappoint. From the high ceilings to the beautiful hardwoods and owners suit on the main floor, this home is a must see. The dining room, living room, office, as well as all the bedrooms were beautifully thought out making the rooms feel grand. Large secondary bedrooms with walk in closets and bathrooms. Keeping room in the Kitchen and living room overlook the magnificent pool and outdoor oasis. This home is an entertainers dream. Don’t miss this opportunity to own this move-in ready home.
